{"tid":756254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港迪士尼最新遊樂設施「蟻俠與黃蜂女：擊戰特攻！」明年登場","createTime":"2018-07-26T01:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T05:46:07.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ea7a0f8c9ec1635438e2d64784370e687f722172","tid":756254,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T01:48:35.000Z","msg":"Marvel迷注意! 香港迪士尼樂園宣佈，將於明年登場的全新Marvel主題遊樂設施，命名為「蟻俠與黃蜂女：擊戰特攻！」，屆時Marvel Studios電影《蟻俠2：黃蜂女現身》中兩位主角Paul Stephen Rudd （保羅活特）和Nicole Evangeline Lilly （伊雲祖蓮莉莉）將會在「蟻俠與黃蜂女：擊戰特攻！」這項互動遊樂設施中亮相。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1Kw76vd5owc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1Kw76vd5owc&d=TbmCC7jMkKUGLVsP2qrxg%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=09beac52\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1Kw76vd5owc</a><br />\n<br />\n香港迪士尼樂園表示，「蟻俠與黃蜂女：擊戰特攻！」是繼2017年開幕的「鐵甲奇俠飛行之旅」後，樂園第2個Marvel主題遊樂設施，位於「史達科技展」旁邊。樂園直至2023年，亦會進行分階段的擴展計劃，陸續推出更多Marvel主題的遊樂體驗，致力打造香港成超級英雄的亞洲基地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2120000/2122982/dl_002_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2120000%2F2122982%2Fdl_002_1024.jpg&h=c63e9aec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2122982/%E8%BF%AA%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%BC%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0Marvel%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E3%80%8C%E8%9F%BB%E4%BF%A0%E8%88%87%E9%BB%83%E8%9C%82%E5%A5%B3%EF%BC%9A%E6%93%8A%E6%88%B0%E7%89%B9%E6%94%BB%EF%BC%81%E3%80%8D%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E7%99%BB%E5%A0%B4%E3%80%90%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87%E3%80%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2122982%2F%25E8%25BF%25AA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%2596%25B0Marvel%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%2588%25B2%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%259F%25BB%25E4%25BF%25A0%25E8%2588%2587%25E9%25BB%2583%25E8%259C%2582%25E5%25A5%25B3%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%2594%25BB%25EF%25BC%2581%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%2